  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ObjectName: Prefab Entity - Load content from another map onto this position
  objectTips:
  - All objects loaded will be parented to the prefab entity
  - Useful for when you want to use the same content in several maps
  - 'Beware, events rely on a hidden ID... '
  - If you want to reuse the same DO entity... then copy and paste the exact same
    entity.
  - Be careful of prefabs that call another prefab... this may lead to confusion
